entry.title: udohjeremiah/ProjectEuler.jl
entry.summary: ProjectEuler.jl is a package that allows offline access to challenging mathematical problems from Project Euler through Julia's REPL. It is a valuable resource for those looking to improve their Julia programming skills while solving interesting mathematical problems.
